#. type: Yaml Front Matter Array Element: tags
#: content/workflows/scene-referred/index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pipeline"
msgstr ""

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: thumbnail
#: content/workflows/scene-referred/index.md:1
